"from\": 629, \"to\": 639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"History So is olympic gold medal actually made entirely of gold?\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"History\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not quite - usually the gold and silver medals are both made of silver.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold and silver medals\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic gold medals are required to be made from at least 92.5% silver, and must contain a minimum of six grams of gold, often as a coating.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 92.5% silver\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"six grams\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"a coating\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the past, Olympic medals were actually made of pure gold until 1912, but after World War One, countries swapped to making silver medals with a layer of gold on top.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"pure gold\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"World War\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"silver medals\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"a layer\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"senten